---
title: Quick Double Pesto Chicken & Courgette Fusilli with Baby Leaves
description: You can add just about anything to a pasta, but sometimes simple and tasty is the way to go. For our favourite twirly-whirly pasta, we recommend a hearty, homey combo of juicy chicken, tender courgette and punchy basil pesto. Grab a fork and take a bite!
